Teachers.Name: Krishna Chaitanya
Teachers.About: Krishna Chaitanya is a simple Yoga Teacher who thinks of himself as an eternal student in awe of the ocean of yoga wisdom. His special expertise is in the field of traditional Hatha Yoga, Meditation, Philosophy and Psychology of Yoga-Vedanta.

Teachers.Name: Lauryne Hartman
Teachers.About: Lauryne is a certified Hatha and Yin yoga instructor who enjoys incorporating mindfulness and meditation into her practice. She has been practicing yoga for over seven years across North America and has a passion for bringing love and light into others lives. As someone who has dealt with anxiety throughout her life, meditation and yoga has been the outlet that allowed Lauryne to find inner peace and calm. She is a firm believer that taking time for you, is one of the greatest gifts you can give yourself.
